Resurrect
Discworld ritual help
Resurrect


.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Resurrect -- Raises a player from the dead.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This ritual raises players from the dead and restores them to 
their former glory.  You need a prayer book, a holy symbol, 
a holy amulet and a relic to perform this ritual.  You can't
perform it on yourself.
.EP

